#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""agent-sandbox - Secure bubblewrap sandbox for AI coding agents.

Isolates AI coding agents (Claude, Codex, Gemini, etc.) so they can only
write to the current project directory and their own sandboxed config.
Protects the host from filesystem damage, credential theft, and process
interference.
"""

